**Search YouTube without the YouTube Data API v3**

A professional, Modern & actively maintained Python library for searching YouTube content‚Äîcompletely free and without youtube data API quotas.

[Features](#-features) ‚Ä¢ [Installation](#-installation) ‚Ä¢ [Quick Start](#-quick-start) ‚Ä¢ [Documentation](#-documentation) ‚Ä¢ [Examples](#-examples) ‚Ä¢ [Testing](#-testing)

